Package net.akami.mask.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MaskOperator<E>
    A specific operation taking an input, sorting out an output.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mask
    Mutable object representing a raw mathematical expression as a string, without any extra information.
    MaskContext
    Definer of a calculation environment, required to perform any operation on expressions.
    MaskDerivativeCalculator
    An overlay to the DerivativeTree system.
    MaskImageCalculator
    Operator used for images of functions computation.
    MaskOperatorHandler
    Highest level object of the operation architecture.
    MaskSimplifier
    An overlay to the ReducerTree system.
